      <title>HarmonyOS_鸿蒙</title>
      <link href="2021/01/27/harmonyos-hong-meng/"/>
      <url>2021/01/27/harmonyos-hong-meng/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><p>title: HarmonyOS_鸿蒙<br>date: 2019-09-07 09:25:00<br>author: 翼龙<br>img:<br>top: true<br>cover: true<br>coverImg:<br>password: 8d969eef6ecad3c29a3a629280e686cf0c3f5d5a86aff3ca12020c923adc6c92<br>toc: true<br>mathjax: false<br>summary: 科技智创未来，分享美好生活！<br>categories: 翼龙家居<br>tags:</p><ul><li>HarmonyOS</li><li>鸿蒙</li><li>keywords: HarmonyOS,鸿蒙<br>reprintPolicy: cc_by</li></ul><hr><p><img src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i2/780616195/O1CN013lM3ke1vdMFctI2zV_!!780616195.png_240x240.jpg"></p><hr><table><thead><tr><th>A</th><th>B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><img src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/780616195/O1CN01T2MsON1vdMFVmyWGD_!!780616195.jpg_240x240.jpg"></td><td><img src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i2/780616195/O1CN018tKRrw1vdMFgqEn65_!!780616195.jpg_240x240.jpg"></td></tr><tr><td>_1</td><td>_2</td></tr><tr><td><img src="https://fly-52elong-bf.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/yifang/yifang_%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83/IMG_20170307_100659.jpg"></td><td><img src="https://fly-52elong-bf.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/yifang/yifang_%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83/IMG_20170307_101016.jpg"></td></tr></tbody></table><hr><p>HarmonyOS是一款“面向未来”、面向全场景（移动办公、运动健康、社交通信、媒体娱乐等）的分布式操作系统。在传统的单设备系统能力的基础上，HarmonyOS提出了基于同一套系统能力、适配多种终端形态的分布式理念，能够支持多种终端设备.</p><h2 id="通知类"><a href="#通知类" class="headerlink" title="通知类"></a>通知类</h2><h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201127130343188.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTI1Mjk4NjA=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70"></h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
